ing: 4 boneless chicken breast halves, cooked and cubed
2 cups condensed cream of celery soup
des: "This is a quick and delicious pop-in-the-oven dinner that your whole family will love! If you like, you can use cream of chicken or cream of mushroom soup, instead of cream of celery. Add a vegetable for color, if desired!"
ins:
In a 9x13 inch baking dish combine the chicken, macaroni, milk, soup, cheese, onions and salt and pepper to taste. Mix all together, cover dish and let sit in refrigerator overnight.
Preheat oven to 350 degrees F (175 degrees C).
Bake at 350 degrees F (175 degrees C) for 1 hour.
